sentences: Screamin' Sirens was an American all-female band from Hollywood, California that recorded from 1983 to 1987.
FormationScreamin' Sirens were formed in Hollywood, California in around 1983.
After going through two bassists who quickly left, Rosie answered the band's ad in the Hollywood Times and tried out for the band in October 1980.
Fur Dixon went on to play in The Cramps, The Dixons, Fur Dixon and Blow Up, Fur Dixon and Steve Werner, and a new band she formed in 2015, WTFUKUSHIMA!
